entries.title_d: The Rebel bombers have decided to try and terminate you instead of retreating. Defeat them, they must be the last of the Rebel fools in the area.
entries.title: Yavin system: The last of them.
entries.complete: Imperial Space Station: < Amazing! Your initiative and selflessnes has saved hundreds of loyal citizens pilot. If you ever visit our beloved Emperor's retreat on Naboo, talk to one of the Imperial pilots outside and they will reward you for your bravery. Station, over and out. >
